Catherine Mouchet https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Catherine_Mouchet 0 Catherine Mouchet (born 21 August 1959) is a French actress. She studied at the Conservatoire de Paris, following the courses of Jacques Lassalle and Claude Régy. Her performance in the film Thérèse, directed by Alain Cavalier, won her the César Award for Most Promising Actress for 1987. Catherine_Mouchet ( born 21_August_1959 ) is a_French_actress .
